Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding your letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Minori Suzuki, voice of Kanade Yoisaki from Nightcord at 25:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In this ProSeka AfterTalk, we'll look back at the event
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,while covering messages you, the fans, have sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this stream is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda want the staff to secretly show me all of them, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really curious about everyone's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be introducing the letters we received during the program, so please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, please post your thoughts on the event and this broadcast with #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also watching the YouTube chat, so if you have anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick up any interesting comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,like 'It was a good story,' or '{i1}Kon-Niigo{i0},' right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's {i1}Kon-Niigo{i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, there's also an AfterLive from 10 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and at 10:05 PM, this event's 3DMV
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will be released, so I want to watch it with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want to proceed strictly on time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I want to watch the story video a bit longer than usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was a little selfish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the story is a bit longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hope you'll all watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's get right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk about the story of "Colors of Pure Sense"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, how was this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look back at it together while introducing your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time doing ProSeka AfterTalk since it was renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been about a year, and a year ago it was probably before the renewal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so this is my first time weaving words from everyone's letters, and I'm a little happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is a letter from Amelia Time-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They said, 'This is my first time sending feedback.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The scene that left an impression on me was Ena deleting her selfie account.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt growth in Ena, who had been running away from facing her art, deciding to face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, like Ena, I was scared to face myself and ran away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ena's positive attitude encouraged me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought I should also do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Minori Suzuki, what feelings did you put into Ena's performance this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Amelia Time-san, thank you for your wonderful letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd like to talk about it later
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,while watching the story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For Ena this time, and when singing N25's recent songs, what I was conscious of as Ena,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and as a cast member, was that I personally made sure
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena wouldn't go back to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,her old self. Because even if slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena is steadily
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,moving forward, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,N25's songs, due to their type, often have negative or backward-looking words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or a certain atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I tried not to be pulled too much by that, and also,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,well, perhaps if it had a bit of a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sad or negative nuance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,honestly, as a song or a line,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it might resonate more with everyone, making them think 'Oh,' or 'I want to hear that,' or
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,'This phrase is nice.' I think there are many things that catch your
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ear and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,stick with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just Suzuki's desire for recognition,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to show something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I try to convey that Ena is slowly but surely looking forward, through her songs and lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even with the same words, I try to make sure you can feel that she's moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm conscious of that, and I gradually increase that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,'forward-looking' aspect based on the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I approached playing her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, for this event and recent songs, Ena understands that the world is warmer than she thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and people around her will help her more than she thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Ena truly understands that now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was conscious of that when performing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure to keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, next, I'd like to introduce one more letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter is from Sudachi Udon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Minori-san, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched "Color of Pure Sense."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What left an impression on me was in Episode 7, the scene where Ena
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is so happy drawing that her emotions soar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena, who could only boost her self-esteem through others' evaluations or selfies, finally realized, 'It's okay to be myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and my expression can be as free as I want it to be.'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As Ena's world gradually became more colorful, and she found joy in drawing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the way her eyes sparkled more and more was powerfully conveyed through Minori-san's voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it brought tears to my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to continue watching over and supporting Ena, who has resolved not to give up on her dreams and her art.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Minori-san, the colors of Ena's heart... Oh, what a wonderful message!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for portraying them so vividly through your vocal performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank {1}you{0} for receiving it so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What I always think is, you know, I hope Ena's feelings reach everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she's a game character,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and a 2D one, but Ena is truly alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's truly living,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena's future,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no one knows what it holds yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I hope I can convey
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that raw, living feeling of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the wonderful feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have a lot I want to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I talk too much here while watching the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll run out of time in 5 minutes, so I want to move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This time too, I've picked out scenes I personally want to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's watch them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I made a selfish request, and when I say 'I made a selfish request',
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the staff members shake their heads a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really conflicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so tempted to watch episodes 7 and 8 together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think we'll just watch
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an AfterTalk, so it's a talk show, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If Minori (me) talking too much
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,bothers you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,please rewatch the story in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's painting, it's sparkling somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it's not the same world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he paint
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you just paint it red?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This leaf doesn't have any red on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it looked better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The colors you see might be different,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to draw it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the colors are completely different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Art is freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own world, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you should draw however you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is this painting Dad's world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What color will you paint next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What will that bird perched on the branch look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's hands, drawing pictures,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,looked like magic, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those hands from back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,those very hands—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put down your brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was always watching, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bring your works to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I admired painters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The hands I saw back then were so big and sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,drawing it exactly like that might be a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's like magic, creating a world on a large canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ena-chan, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it look
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to me back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the competition results are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen them yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I express them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Big, filling the entire canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I got a bit sidetracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we go see them together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm curious what kind of paintings everyone else drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The sparkling colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll add the color of the tree my dad painted back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not green,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but red running through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the colors got mixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I was able to express it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this is my touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This might actually be better, giving it a magical feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The world I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Painting is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...freedom, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll paint it however I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll intentionally layer many colors, letting them mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,scoring and evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I should paint even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so it sparkles with all sorts of colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit hard to talk, but it's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsuno-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's a game, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it to be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you all to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.04,0:22:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,my whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm consciously performing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you seem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she's found her own answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of painting it will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.36,0:25:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Yoisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.88,0:25:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ena-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.44,0:25:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.52,0:25:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.84,0:25:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She was here just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.00,0:25:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.40,0:25:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.24,0:26:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.16,0:26:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.68,0:26:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.40,0:26:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was time for our meeting, so I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.48,0:26:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.64,0:26:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.64,0:26:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.28,0:26:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to get some fresh air outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.04,0:26:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.84,0:26:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.92,0:26:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.40,0:26:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,about the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.72,0:26:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.96,0:26:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That painting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.84,0:26:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.80,0:26:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.68,0:26:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it was really enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.36,0:26:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.76,0:26:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,drawing has often been
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.00,0:27:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a struggle, but this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.04,0:27:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it was truly enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.92,0:27:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Sensei, I was able to give it my all,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.92,0:27:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel like I painted a picture I'm truly satisfied with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.56,0:27:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.40,0:27:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.92,0:27:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.80,0:27:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.84,0:27:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.72,0:27:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,still,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.40,0:27:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if that was
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.68,0:27:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And even then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,if it still doesn't reach P,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.88,0:27:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.20,0:27:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.68,0:27:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I had always
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.84,0:28:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to go
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.72,0:28:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to Toubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.84,0:28:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to study art
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.20,0:28:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at Japan's best institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.96,0:28:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.12,0:28:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But the people aiming for Toubi can draw much better than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.88,0:28:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I had to be good enough to get results in competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.64,0:28:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I gave it my all,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.24,0:28:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I still only got a C.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.68,0:28:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But even then,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,even with all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.40,0:28:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to go to Toubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.60,0:29:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.24,0:29:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel like someone like me shouldn't even aim for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.52,0:29:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.76,0:29:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, your skill is insufficient to aim for Toubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.16,0:29:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.60,0:29:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,your world was undoubtedly depicted in that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.92,0:29:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that all art techniques can be explained by theory, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.88,0:29:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I also mentioned that there's an appeal in art that can't be measured by theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.32,0:29:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,While evaluations are based on theory, how much a painting touches people's hearts is a different kind of assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.92,0:30:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the Toubi entrance exam, evaluations beyond theory are also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.20,0:30:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.56,0:30:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if Shinonome-san can further hone her strengths,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.76,0:30:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the possibility of passing the Toubi exam is not zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.80,0:30:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.44,0:30:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.32,0:30:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the current Shinonome-san lacks too many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.12,0:30:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The current C grade indicates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.56,0:30:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, if Shinonome-san wishes to proceed, I will teach you what you need to reach your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.76,0:30:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.48,0:30:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.96,0:30:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.72,0:30:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.16,0:30:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.00,0:30:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.48,0:31:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Akihiro-sensei got a voice, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.40,0:31:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go to Toubi,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.00,0:31:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I could never bring myself to commit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.44,0:31:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept making excuses, saying I wasn't skilled enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.72,0:31:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.68,0:31:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.12,0:31:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.00,0:31:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,aim for Toubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.64,0:31:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.32,0:31:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll face many setbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.48,0:31:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My lack of skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.84,0:31:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,will become even more frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.00,0:31:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to face art more seriously than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.36,0:31:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.32,0:31:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.44,0:32:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I still can't quite break the habit of escaping
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.36,0:32:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to selfies when things get tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.60,0:32:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this time, it almost happened so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.96,0:32:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I'm going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.36,0:32:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,more serious than ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.92,0:32:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.28,0:32:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.04,0:32:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.92,0:32:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.20,0:32:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at it like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.40,0:32:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels like an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:32:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.44,0:33:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.56,0:33:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.72,0:33:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.84,0:33:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.60,0:33:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,everything until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.60,0:33:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.68,0:33:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time, so I guess I'll start working on Niigo stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.56,0:33:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ena-chan's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.36,0:33:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.20,0:33:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena, Ena, Ena!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.80,0:33:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.84,0:33:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.36,0:33:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.36,0:33:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've always known.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.00,0:33:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has your account been hacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.48,0:33:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.72,0:33:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena probably made various decisions and resolved herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.44,0:33:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.68,0:33:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,her account, the one with the selfies,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.16,0:33:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,she still ended up relying on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.92,0:33:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,using them as an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.60,0:34:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But she couldn't escape, and she still wanted to go to Toubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.48,0:34:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't have enough confidence to tell others, or to truly resolve herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.60,0:34:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.08,0:34:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,she was able to properly quit and make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.96,0:34:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from here on, it'll be tough, but it's like the fog in her heart cleared, bringing a sense of relief,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.68,0:34:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and also the feeling that there's still
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.56,0:34:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,more to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.92,0:34:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With all those mixed feelings, somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.76,0:34:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there was also a relieved Ena, and that's what I felt strongly towards the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.12,0:34:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about that while acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.48,0:34:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason why I chose episodes 7 and 8
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.84,0:34:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is because of her father. There were many things that happened, and times when she couldn't face him,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.56,0:35:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but she really
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,admires him. Probably, after puberty and various events,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.36,0:35:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,her father also wasn't very good with words,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.64,0:35:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and she realized that the respect she secretly held for her father, despite her frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.28,0:35:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was still there. As Ena took a step forward as an artist,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.56,0:35:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,she remembered that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.16,0:35:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I also got to play young Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.04,0:35:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But because she was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.64,0:35:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,she was pure, and everything she saw was new and sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.16,0:35:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that world, her father was there, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.08,0:35:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,father was an even more amazing person to Ena, someone she admired, someone who created incredible things,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.08,0:35:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,like a block of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.84,0:36:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like she was talking to such a figure, or the amazingness of the paintings her father created,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.36,0:36:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.72,0:36:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.36,0:36:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.48,0:36:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I acted while feeling all of that, I was able to maintain that sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.00,0:36:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and return to that scene where she's drawing, without really breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.04,0:36:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,character. So, holding onto that sparkle and the scenery she saw with her father,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.72,0:36:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,being able to go into the scene where she happily draws was personally very
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,significant. And she was able to truly say "fun" for the first time. That was probably very significant for Ena too,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.76,0:36:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it's still in the middle of the path she's finally reached, she finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.24,0:36:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it felt. Ah, I'm about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.00,0:36:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also why...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.56,0:36:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.60,0:37:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw the script,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.28,0:37:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I cried so much at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.92,0:37:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, "It's finally good, isn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.56,0:37:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, a broadcast mishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.12,0:37:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.44,0:37:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, for five years... well, not five years in Ena's timeline, but
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.00,0:37:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there are so many different feelings, and I think many of you can really relate to Ena's
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.48,0:37:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,story. I also understand her feelings very well because I'm in that world of art, where there's no single right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.48,0:37:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I understand her feelings so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.44,0:37:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not just that; it's also that Ena's hard work, somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.56,0:37:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,her efforts are finally being rewarded, or rather, 'rewarded' might be too simple a word, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.08,0:37:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but I was so happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.24,0:37:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first read the script, even I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.92,0:38:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,cried with a feeling of 'Congratulations, Suzuki!' And while reading, it was Ena's 'Ah, I finally made it this far!'
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.44,0:38:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that simple feeling she achieved, that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,something that had been tense from all her hard work finally loosened. Ah, excuse me, there are a lot of tissues here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.04,0:38:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so, with those feelings, naturally,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.80,0:38:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,while shedding tears, there were parts where my words got choked up, but that's
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.52,0:38:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,acting, and it's truly the good part about playing Ena, that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.52,0:38:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if I cried as Ena, Ena would cry with me, and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, they adjusted to my pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.64,0:38:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the lines move forward when you press a button, but until that button is pressed, they truly
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.00,0:38:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,do everything carefully without cutting anything. I'm just so grateful and moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.20,0:39:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the feedback for this event was that it was a really, really good
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.04,0:39:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,story, and I received many comments saying that. And also, it wasn't about Suzuki-san's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.12,0:39:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,acting being like this, or Suzuki-san's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,voice being like that. Instead of me, everyone truly accepted Ena's way of life, and somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.64,0:39:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they were happy, or felt encouraged, or
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.76,0:39:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thought 'Let's do our best together,' or simply those who had always supported Ena,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,those people were
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.88,0:39:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,like, 'Oh, that's good,' or 'But it's still just the beginning,' and they expressed various emotions towards Ena,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.68,0:39:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that they did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.64,0:39:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy that I could pour all of my current effort
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.76,0:39:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,into Ena, and I'm glad I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.64,0:39:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.76,0:39:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.64,0:39:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.20,0:39:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's take a look at the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.52,0:40:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, for Ena, who kept facing art and suffering because of what she loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.04,0:40:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the moment she saw a glimmer of hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.08,0:40:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why I chose it, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.28,0:40:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.24,0:40:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in about four quick minutes, I'd like us to take a look at the card illustrations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.32,0:40:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we look at the illustrations, we've actually received comments
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.24,0:40:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,from the illustration production team about the outfits, so I'd like to share them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.00,0:40:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.04,0:40:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, Ena struggled to get into art school,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.08,0:40:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,almost gave up when she couldn't reach her desired level, but didn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.04,0:40:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This story was the central theme, and we created the design with an art apron over a school uniform as the motif,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.60,0:40:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,imagining Ena's style as a student preparing for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.48,0:40:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.52,0:40:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,While there are aprons in existing outfits for an artist style,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.84,0:40:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for this event's outfit, only Ena has a patched-up apron,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.00,0:40:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which represents her perseverance despite repeatedly facing setbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.72,0:40:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This design incorporates unique arrangements for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.60,0:41:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.20,0:41:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, while retaining strong elements of a school uniform like the sailor collar and pleats,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.88,0:41:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we've consciously added shape arrangements to enhance the costume feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.20,0:41:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.96,0:41:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here are the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.96,0:41:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, the untrained version. Everyone gave this one a great response.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.80,0:41:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's drawing happily, her hands are dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.72,0:41:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.20,0:41:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, this is the wonderful untrained version of everyone who watched over and supported Ena this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.20,0:41:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the untrained and trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.72,0:41:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Kanade is, after all, someone who creates things,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.24,0:41:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so even though the genre is different, she understands Ena's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.36,0:41:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And KAITO-san. KAITO-san also gave Ena many important words.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.56,0:41:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're all eating ice cream together,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.80,0:41:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so please take a look if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.44,0:42:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm calling it 'yogurt ice cream'.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.48,0:42:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I like yogurt ice cream, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.88,0:42:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's me again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.12,0:42:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.80,0:42:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.60,0:42:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of wonderful art.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.08,0:42:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're eating ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.92,0:42:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.00,0:42:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.44,0:42:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, Mafuyu-chan. Ah, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.28,0:42:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,wait, wait, wait, I can't long-press!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.64,0:42:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.60,0:42:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's holding an apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.24,0:42:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.80,0:42:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.08,0:42:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.60,0:42:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, you've seen the illustrations before and after training. Ugh, how many times am I going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.56,0:42:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.48,0:42:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I still have a few minutes to talk about the story, so I will. The previous story wasn't really about Ena's art,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.60,0:42:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.72,0:42:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one before that, the one where I sang "I am the Rain"—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.12,0:43:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that song was also about Ena's art. I don't like saying "Ena's drawings."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.40,0:43:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, for that story about her art,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.40,0:43:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to go to a museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.52,0:43:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was able to portray what it means to look at art, based on my own experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.64,0:43:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got to know Ena better. This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.52,0:43:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to be walking along, humming to myself, and I saw Ena walking by. There was probably a school for art students,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.84,0:43:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,people aiming for a career in art,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.00,0:43:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,on that street. I thought, "Oh, so this is what it's like." Just observing from the side, I felt such intense tension,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.80,0:43:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and realized how incredibly strict that world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.16,0:43:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I went into the recording session with that renewed feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.48,0:43:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can convey even a little bit of the atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.04,0:43:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the "texture" of Ena's world, to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.96,0:43:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I strive for every day when I perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.68,0:43:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.36,0:43:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.84,0:44:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.60,0:44:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there are still
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.48,0:44:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a few tens of seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.68,0:44:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, some of you might have already watched the AfterLive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.08,0:44:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's content that takes place after the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.08,0:44:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena's refreshed expression—though she still has many challenges ahead—
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.92,0:44:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,her determined expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.40,0:44:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and her singing voice, I hope they're reaching you all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.12,0:44:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be so happy if they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.96,0:44:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.92,0:44:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.16,0:44:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.16,0:44:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena is truly loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.52,0:44:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To receive such a wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.68,0:44:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, with that, after watching the 3DMV that was created for this event,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.68,0:44:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk about the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.12,0:44:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.08,0:44:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.80,0:45:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A body that can't become anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.72,0:45:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing within a borrowed life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.96,0:45:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I dive deep inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.88,0:45:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,even now, my past self
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.40,0:45:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is still smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.48,0:45:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back, what clearly remains
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.00,0:45:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are fragments of a dream that sprouted in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.52,0:45:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast into two shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.96,0:45:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that past eventually turned into dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.16,0:45:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in dwelling on
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.36,0:46:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a past that has changed like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.88,0:46:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.88,0:46:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A truly small,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.96,0:46:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.16,0:46:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,light…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.76,0:46:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The feelings I believed in
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.28,0:46:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,still haven't reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.68,0:46:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, remaining parched,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.24,0:46:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to draw more of the future with these hands onto the pure white scenery before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.84,0:46:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.88,0:46:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.20,0:46:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.28,0:46:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.92,0:46:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this world reflected in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.56,0:47:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, excuse me, my screen... pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.64,0:47:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The song written for this event by Choucho-P,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.72,0:47:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,its title is...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.44,0:47:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time the title is revealed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.12,0:47:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of that picture is... a 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.44,0:47:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.76,0:47:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First, uh, oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.28,0:47:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment, I thought my own notes were Choucho-P's comments,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.36,0:47:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was like 'huh?', but they weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.52,0:47:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my notes that I sent to the staff beforehand. Okay, I'll read them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.48,0:47:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, just by listening, I can feel Ena's journey, and it makes me tear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.60,0:47:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The title contains 'e' and 'na', her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.00,0:47:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt it was truly a song that depicted Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.72,0:47:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrets, frustrating feelings, painful feelings—
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.44,0:48:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than just being pessimistic, I sang it with the resolve to turn them into strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.96,0:48:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and with the positive feelings of her having made that resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.20,0:48:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my past self emailed to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.64,0:48:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Choucho-P's comments are introduced on ProSeka Broadcast Station and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.72,0:48:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think they're also on Twitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.72,0:48:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or X, so please check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.08,0:48:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, with those feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.72,0:48:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, there are lyrics that feel like she's looking back at the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.20,0:48:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but, well, it's like the Ena of today
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.12,0:48:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is truly looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.68,0:48:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, Ena probably definitely has regrets, but she's also a girl who understands
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.60,0:48:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that she is who she is because of those experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.04,0:48:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even the phrases looking back at the past, I didn't want to sing them
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.68,0:48:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with the full intensity of past Ena's suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.12,0:48:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I sang with that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.92,0:49:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and as I mentioned earlier, in the story, her resolve was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.16,0:49:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I sang with a sense of relief and the bright feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.12,0:49:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of finally understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.88,0:49:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but this isn't the goal yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.12,0:49:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's a start, I really focused on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.36,0:49:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that feeling of being in the middle, you know, that kind of sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.64,0:49:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I sang it with that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.48,0:49:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, rather than a huge emotional outburst,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.16,0:49:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really focused on quietly, internally, playing out the words,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.76,0:49:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,encouraging myself, you know, like patting my own chest and saying 'I can do it!'
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.76,0:49:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I sang it with that kind of self-encouragement in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.28,0:49:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I just end up crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.48,0:49:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can listen to the full version, since I'm the one who sang it, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.76,0:49:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, I just cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.16,0:49:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.88,0:50:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This story and this song, they just make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.08,0:50:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.64,0:50:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I wouldn't cry this time talking about this, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.96,0:50:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.04,0:50:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for those of you out there who are a little jealous that I said I can hear the full version,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.24,0:50:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.56,0:50:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The 2DMV for this commissioned song, 'Sono E no Namae wa,' will also be uploaded
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.20,0:50:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to the ProSeka official YouTube channel at 10:15 PM after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.68,0:50:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, along with the 3DMV, please be sure to check
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.72,0:50:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.72,0:50:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that means we'll probably be able to hear the full version, right, if the 2DMV is like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.08,0:50:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.88,0:50:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even seen the 2DMV yet myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.64,0:50:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and speaking of the 3DMV, though it's a bit late, my thoughts are that even though it's filmed in full,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.04,0:50:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the vocal distribution, so I know which parts are Ena's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.44,0:50:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.48,0:50:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And since the song starts with the three members of N25 in order,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.68,0:51:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,my imaginary 3DMV, the one in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.04,0:51:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, 'Ah, not Ena, but the song...'
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.88,0:51:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,'How will it start?' I wondered if all four or five members
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.76,0:51:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,would suddenly appear, or if it would start with Mizuki's opening line,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.48,0:51:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.88,0:51:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena was featured prominently throughout,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.60,0:51:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course, for those who support other characters,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.36,0:51:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy if their screen time was high too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.60,0:51:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But this MV really put a lot of spotlight on Ena,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.84,0:51:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and it matched the story so well. I felt it was an MV that truly captured
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.12,0:51:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena's way of life, and as a performer,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.16,0:51:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was incredibly happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.16,0:51:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.72,0:51:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a really great feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.00,0:51:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena being featured is always the case, but for the song during Ena's story,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.40,0:51:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the setting also felt like it was gradually rising to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.20,0:51:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And that, well, this is just a fan's theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.60,0:51:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was happy about that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.84,0:52:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the location itself was moving upwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.08,0:52:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I found that really heartwarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.60,0:52:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the location itself was moving upwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.76,0:52:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I found that really heartwarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.96,0:52:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've only seen it a few times myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.44,0:52:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to watch it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.12,0:52:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm really looking forward to the 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.88,0:52:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.40,0:52:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.12,0:52:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anything I've left unsaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.36,0:52:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've entrusted everything to Ena's voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.44,0:52:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to Ena herself. So, more than anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.52,0:52:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can feel Ena's way of life through the song
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.80,0:52:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.20,0:52:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue to support Ena, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.64,0:52:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much to everyone who supports Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.84,0:52:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm not Ena, as someone who plays her,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.96,0:52:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm a close presence to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.28,0:52:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll continue to do my best every day as an actress
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.96,0:53:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to properly portray her as she grows even more
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.68,0:53:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,after making this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.76,0:53:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue to watch over Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.00,0:53:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.44,0:53:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, though it was a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.32,0:53:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this ProSeka AfterTalk…
